name: Wooden Ocean
description: Combat horrific monsters, construct a giant town, and uncover countless secrets in this unique open RPG. Good luck, and don't die too much.
minimum_requirements: OS: Windows 7 or Greater Processor: Intel Core 2 1.06Ghz Memory: 1 GB RAM Graphics: Integrated graphics DirectX: Version 9.0 Storage: 1 GB available space
recommended_requirements: OS: Windows 7 or Greater Processor: Intel Core 3 2.0Ghz Graphics: Integrated graphics DirectX: Version 10 Storage: 2 GB available space
